# VolunteerIQ — Implementation Plan

> **Goal:** Build the complete VolunteerIQ frontend MVP from the provided DESIGN.md, APP_FLOW.md, and DATABASE_SCHEMA.md specifications.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Scope Decision:** This plan builds the **full frontend with hardcoded mock data**. Backend integration (Supabase DB, Gemini AI parsing, Resend email, auth) is **deferred** to a separate phase. This lets us nail the UI/UX first.

> [!WARNING]
> **Tailwind Version:** The DESIGN.md includes a `tailwind.config.js` (v3 style), but the Tailwind skill recommends CSS-first v4. I'll use **Tailwind v4 with `@theme` directives** for the design tokens. The color/font values remain identical.

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Screens to build in this phase:** Landing Page, Dashboard (3-panel), Volunteer Assignment Detail, 404/500 error pages, and Login/Register forms. The full admin panel and onboarding tour will be scaffolded but can be completed in a follow-up.

