### Phase 5 — Core Features & Interactivity

#### [NEW] `lib/mock-data.ts`
- 8-12 realistic needs across Maharashtra districts
- Mix of urgency levels (2 critical, 3 high, 4 medium, 2 resolved)
- 10-15 volunteers with skills, availability, locations
- Pre-computed matches (3 per need)
- Activity log entries
- Organization + coordinator data

#### Dashboard state management (in `app/(app)/dashboard/page.tsx`)
- `selectedNeedId` state synced to URL `?need={id}`
- Filter state (urgency toggles)
- Search query with 300ms debounce
- Need click → card highlight + pin highlight + right panel load
- Pin click → same behavior + scroll left panel to card
- Filter toggle → instant JS filter on both list and map pins
- Assign flow → button state change + toast + stats update
- Resolve flow → confirmation modal → state updates

#### Parse simulation
- Textarea input → Parse button click
- Phase 1→2→3→4 UX flow from DESIGN.md §10
- Simulated 2-3s delay → toast transition → new pin + card

