### Phase 7 — Polish & Accessibility

#### Animations
- All `@keyframes` from DESIGN.md §12 implemented in globals.css
- `prefers-reduced-motion` disables non-essential animations
- Stats counter tick (JS `requestAnimationFrame`)

#### Keyboard Shortcuts
- `/` → focus search
- `Escape` → close modal/deselect/clear search  
- `↑`/`↓` → navigate needs list
- `A` → assign top volunteer
- `R` → resolve (opens modal)

#### Accessibility
- ARIA labels on all interactive elements
- `role="list"` / `role="listitem"` on needs list
- Focus ring: `box-shadow: 0 0 0 2px rgba(83,82,237,0.5)`
- Modal focus trap
- Map: `role="img"` with descriptive `aria-label`
- Toast: `aria-live` regions
- Tab order follows topbar → left panel → center → right panel

#### Mobile Polish
- Bottom sheet component for map pin tap
- Touch targets ≥ 44×44px
- Pull-to-refresh on needs list
- Responsive topbar (stats hidden on mobile)

