## Open Questions

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **1. Should I build this as a full Next.js app or a simpler Vite SPA?**
> The spec says Next.js, but since we're using mock data (no SSR/API routes needed yet), a Vite app would be faster to scaffold. I'll proceed with Next.js as specified unless you prefer otherwise.

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **2. Which Tailwind version?**
> The DESIGN.md has a `tailwind.config.js` (v3 style). `create-next-app` currently ships Tailwind v4 with CSS-first `@theme`. I'll use **Tailwind v4** since it's the current default. Let me know if you want v3.

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **3. Phase scope — what to build first?**
> This is a large project. I recommend building **Phases 1-5** (Foundation → Design System → Components → Map → Dashboard Interactivity) as the first deliverable, then Phases 6-7 (Additional screens + polish) as follow-up. This gets the core dashboard working first. Agree?

